The paper deals with image reconstruction, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of perceptual and adversarial losses suggests that the paper may also fall under graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) categories. The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could place it under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) categories.
